<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title><%= title %></title>

  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #1a1a1a, #000);
      font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      color: #e0e0e0;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .scanlines {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background: repeating-linear-gradient(
        rgba(255,255,255,0.02),
        rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 2px,
        rgba(0,0,0,0.07) 4px
      );
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 10;
    }

    .container {
      height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      animation: fadeIn 1s ease;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      color: #00eaff;
      text-shadow: 0 0 12px #00eaff;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      animation: glitch 2s infinite;
      position: relative;
    }

    @keyframes glitch {
      0% { transform: translate(0); }
      20% { transform: translate(-2px,2px); }
      40% { transform: translate(2px,-2px); }
      60% { transform: translate(-1px,1px); }
      80% { transform: translate(1px,-1px); }
      100% { transform: translate(0); }
    }

    .card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      padding: 25px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,255,255,0.2);
      box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,255,255,0.2);
      max-width: 600px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      animation: slideUp 1s ease-out;
    }

    @keyframes slideUp {
      from { transform: translateY(30px); opacity: 0; }
      to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
    }

    p { font-size: 18px; }

    .error {
      color: #ff4d6d;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-shadow: 0 0 8px #ff4d6d;
    }

    a {
      color: #00eaff;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: 0.2s;
    }

    a:hover {
      color: #fff;
      text-shadow: 0 0 12px #fff;
    }

  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="scanlines"></div>

  <div class="container">

    <h1>ESCAPE GAME NESTJS</h1>

    <div class="card">
      <p>Bienvenue dans l’Escape Game NestJS.</p>
      <p>Votre première mission est disponible.</p>
      <a href="/level1">Commencer le Niveau 1</a>
      <p><em>L’agence compte sur vous.</em></p>
    </div>
    

  </div>

</body>
</html>
